&lt;li&gt;汉化分享日：&lt;strong&gt;2025-10-17&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;changelog&#34;&gt;Changelog
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;details&gt;
&lt;summary&gt;更新日志&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This patch includes 2 new NSFW scenes for Noah and 5 new ones for Asami.
You can now work out at the gym, and if your Strength is 5 or higher,
you might find Asami there at night&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Asami’s been around since the early builds, but I kept delaying her update for a while.
Honestly, her story might be a bit divisive - some people might love it, others might not
Still, since the game’s heading toward its ending,
I think it’s finally time to move forward with her part.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
